{"tid":2297154,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[轉貼高登] 美國Dominino投票機同香港有關","createTime":"2020-11-23T05:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T00:03:28.000Z","uid":134093,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"050a71a910f623a747da0d24cbd45991b8681ad1","tid":2297154,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:27:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/thread/7331954/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7331954%2Fpage%2F1&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=618dad10\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/thread/7331954/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJB惹南巴貼出一個IT人發現美國Dominion投票機懷疑share <a href=\"http://file到dominionvotingsystems.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffile%E5%88%B0dominionvotingsystems.com&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=6914c4f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">file到dominionvotingsystems.com</a>。嗰個網連去一個喺香港叫AS132839 Power Line Datacenter。<br />\n投票機網同博鰲論壇用過同一ip。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zknnE48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzknnE48.jpg&h=1a7baf21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIT人Twatter: <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/schaumby/status/1329095195498078210?prefetchtimestamp=1605992413081\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fschaumby%2Fstatus%2F1329095195498078210%3Fprefetchtimestamp%3D1605992413081&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=9c5c2072\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fschaumby%2Fstatus%2F1329095195498078210%3Fprefetchtimestamp%3D1605992413081&h=1c03e3d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/schaumby/status/1329095195498078210?prefetchtimestamp=1605992413081</a><br />\n<br />\nAS132839 Powerline Data Center有兩個登記地址，一個係葵涌恆亞中心7樓，另一個係旺角凱途發展中心704室。睇嗰個IT人嘅Twatter圈住嗰個地點，似係恆亞中心。而之前搵倒嗰個喺葵涌Marvel 工業大廈嘅Powerline HK Co Limited，似係office。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ipinfo.io/AS132839/103.233.248.0/24\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fipinfo.io%2FAS132839%2F103.233.248.0%2F24&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=0bf3a233\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ipinfo.io/AS132839/103.233.248.0/24</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://bgpview.io/asn/132839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbgpview.io%2Fasn%2F132839&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=9177ae6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bgpview.io/asn/132839</a><br />\n<br />\n喺網上搵凱途發展大廈704室，見倒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bhUQOYv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbhUQOYv.jpg&h=aa6aea80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一Google富華國際，不得了！<br />\n<br />\n陳麗華，女，滿族，1941年出生於北京頤和園，正黃旗世家，美國佐治亞州薩凡那藝術設計學院榮譽博士，現任全國政協委員，富華國際集團董事局主席，中國紫檀博物館館長，北京滿學會終身名譽會長。<br />\n陳麗華的富華國際集團在北京擁有數家房地產企業，包括長安俱樂部、麗苑公寓等，總投資超過35億。2012年入選美國《時代》雜誌年度最有影響力人物百強榜。<br />\n<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%AF%8C%E5%8D%8E%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E9%9B%86%E5%9B%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbaike.baidu.com%2Fitem%2F%25E5%25AF%258C%25E5%258D%258E%25E5%259B%25BD%25E9%2599%2585%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%259B%25A2&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=b975b1c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%AF%8C%E5%8D%8E%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E9%9B%86%E5%9B%A2</a><br />\n<br />\n再搵陳麗華同喬治亞州薩凡那藝術學院...<br />\n陳麗華個名係用廣東話拼音，百度百科寫住<br />\n深水埗薩凡那藝術學院係同一機構<br />\n<a href=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/2qqlnsm5.s31ibczu5hm.j525b1yopat.0vb.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2F2qqlnsm5.s31ibczu5hm.j525b1yopat.0vb.jpg&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=285e747a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/2qqlnsm5.s31ibczu5hm.j525b1yopat.0vb.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n再搵吓喬治亞州薩凡那市，勁有趣！薩凡那市就係扔投票機喺路邊嘅市！"},{"pid":"f0f973815192f447ca2cd3c1c1cb695edf5c4236","tid":2297154,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f99ca4ce8b5ac7b815973c7930554de9ed7e303","tid":2297154,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b76a8c8ca965456c50aedd5ddebf876005b6906","tid":2297154,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a172f2d1a68111bfb5db9247da31f8b5c6b8ce","tid":2297154,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351731ed9ff8b531247ca4996c5e1b0d6eda6319","tid":2297154,"uid":168492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e91adcc9d6fe85689f7aae540e94f94237b97fb","tid":2297154,"uid":123264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:32:15.000Z","msg":"高登呢獲咁高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f3e491b9a6db8940ecf4adda8c926d58647c47","tid":2297154,"uid":158888,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:33:03.000Z","msg":"鮑威爾statement 証實咗香港有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TfwWKyQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfwWKyQ.jpg&h=678e2f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://parl